# PROXIES FILE (OPTIONAL)
#
# Format: wallet_number, ip:port:username:password
#
# Examples:
# 1, 123.45.67.89:8080:myuser:mypass
# 2, 98.76.54.32:3128:myuser:mypass
# 3, proxy.example.com:8080:myuser:mypass
#
# The wallet_number must match a wallet in wallets.txt
# Wallets without a proxy entry will connect directly (no proxy)
# If you don't need proxies, delete this file or leave it empty

